Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.800
 Video tutorial for the PlayMemories Camera AppsTM [Sync to Smartphone] app (iPhone/iPad) 

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:08.400
 Install the [Sync to Smartphone] app of PlayMemories Camera AppsTM on your camera. 

00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:11.500
 Install the latest version of PlayMemories MobileTM on your smartphone. 

00:00:12.300 --> 00:00:15.500
 Register iPhone/iPad on camera for ILCE-7 

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:57.100
 [SSID] and [Password] will appear on the camera. 

00:00:58.300 --> 00:01:08.700
 Open the Wi-Fi settings screen of your iPhone/iPad. 

00:01:09.400 --> 00:01:17.900
 Set up a Wi-Fi connection for your iPhone/iPad. 

00:01:18.600 --> 00:01:25.000
 Select the detected camera (DIRECT-xxxx: xxx-xxx). 

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:36.300
 Enter the password displayed on your iPhone/iPad into your smartphone. 

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:50.100
 The camera will connect to the iPhone/iPad. 

00:01:50.600 --> 00:02:01.800
 Launch PlayMemories MobileTM on your iPhone/iPad. 

00:02:02.300 --> 00:02:06.900
 Register the camera to automatically transfer still images on PlayMemories MobileTM. 

00:02:14.700 --> 00:02:17.800
 The camera is registered. 

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:46.100
 Follow these steps to return to the shooting screen. 

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:49.800
 Take still images and automatically transfer them to your iPhone/iPad 

00:02:50.700 --> 00:02:58.900
 Use the camera to take still images. 

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:05.600
 Take an iPhone/iPad that has been registered as the transmission destination to a location close to the camera. 

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:10.900
 Turn off the camera. 

00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:25.200
 From the Wi-Fi settings screen, select the camera's SSID and check the Wi-Fi connection. 

00:03:25.900 --> 00:03:38.800
 Return to the main screen and launch PlayMemories MobileTM. The camera will transmit a still image. 

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:43.500
 The camera will automatically turn off when the transfer is complete. 

00:03:52.500 --> 00:03:56.300
 View still images that have been transferred to your iPhone/iPad 

00:03:56.900 --> 00:04:10.200
 You can use the app to view the transmitted still images. 

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:16.300
 You can use the [Sync to Smartphone] app of PlayMemories Camera AppsTM. 

